    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know... i've had cramps like this before and usually they just go away with some meds. i really dont want to go to the er if i dont have to, it's expensive and the wait is always hours. are u sure its not just gas? i feel like if i just take a decent dose of something strong, the pain will settle down by morning and i wont have to deal with doctors.",
