    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but honestly it just feels like bloating too... i've been so stressed lately and my stomach has been all messed up. if i just take a heavy dose of ibuprofen or maybe some nurofen plus, can't i just wait and see how i feel in the morning? i'm pretty sure i can just sleep through it if i get enough meds in me. what's the worst that could happen if i just try to manage it at home for a few hours?",
